  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, randomized, multicenter study to provide additional information on the
      safety and efficacy of the WATCHMAN LAA Closure Technology.

      The PREVAIL study was amended to initiate a prospective, non-randomized continued access
      study titled &quot;Continued Access to PREVAIL (CAP2)&quot; to collect additional information on the
      safety and efficacy of the WATCHMAN LAA closure technology. The study is estimated to enroll
      an initial cohort of 300 subjects with a maximum of 1500 subjects, at 60 investigational
      sites in the U.S.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
